OL,5,CHuw Edwards
OL,7,FActor Martin Clunes is set to play Huw
OL,8,FEdwards in a new drama documenting the
OL,9,Fdownfall of the disgraced former BBC
OL,10,Fpresenter.
OL,12,FIn September 2024, Edwards was
OL,13,Fsentenced to six months imprisonment,
OL,14,Fsuspended for two years, after
OL,15,Fpleading guilty to accessing indecent
OL,16,Fimages of children as young as seven.
