OL,3,CNew drama announced documenting
OL,4,Cdownfall of disgraced BBC presenter
OL,5,CHuw Edwards
OL,7,FBefore his criminal conviction,
OL,8,FEdwards' downfall started after a
OL,9,Freport by the Sun Newspaper in July
OL,10,F2023 alleged that a "top BBC star" had
OL,11,Fpaid a 17-year-old for sexual
OL,12,Fpictures. Days later his wife named
OL,13,Fhim as the presenter at the centre of
OL,14,Fthe scandal and the newsreader
OL,15,Fresigned the following April.
