OL,3,CNew drama announced documenting
OL,4,Cdownfall of disgraced BBC presenter
OL,5,CHuw Edwards
OL,7,FNow '5', formerly Channel 5, have
OL,8,Fcommissioned a two-part factual drama
OL,9,Fwhich says it will recount the
OL,10,Fpresenter's "double life" featuring
OL,11,Finterviews from those who first
OL,12,Freported the story.
OL,14,FThe series, which has a working title
OL,15,Fof Power: The Downfall of Huw Edwards,
OL,16,Fis the first collaboration between 5's
OL,17,Ffactual and scripted commissioning
OL,18,Fteams.
