OL,7,FThey say the drama will reportedly
OL,8,Fbuild on extensive factual research
OL,9,Fover 12 months, and includes extensive
OL,10,Ffirst hand interviews and co-operation
OL,11,Ffrom those at the heart of the scandal
OL,12,Fand exclusive access to The Sun
OL,13,Fnewspaper's award-winning
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FBen Frow, Chief Content Officer, 5
OL,17,Fsaid: "This is an important and
OL,18,Fshocking story ` of how a man in a
OL,19,Fposition of power and trust betrayed
OL,20,Fthat status.
